room_title: Escape room "Quarantine" by Escape It Houston in Houston
room_address: 11501 Sam Houston Ste. B, Humble, TX 77396
room_description: As soon as you enter the research facility G.O.L.D., where the lead scientists work on developing biological weapons, you know there will be no going back. The doors lock behind you, and the radio blasts a message saying you've been exposed to a deadly virus. Will you survive the Quarantine before the damage to your health is irreversible?
